text: Hawk's Nest or Hawks Nest may refer to: *Hawks Nest, New South Wales, a small coastal village in Australia *Hawk's Nest, New York, a scenic overlook near Port Jervis, New York, USA *Hawks Nest, West Virginia, a recreation area in Hawks Nest State Park near Ansted, West Virginia, USA *Hawk's Nest (novel), a 1941 novel *The Hawk's Nest, NCAA men's basketball student section for the University of Iowa Hawkeyes
title: Hawks Nest
